title: Pro Junior (Kitchen Sink)
description:
Don Dohler's Pro Junior

The name Don Dohler might be best associated with low-budget horror cinema like Alien Factor and Nightbeast

But before the DIY entrepreneur went into the film business he was a underground publisher, who made up the character Pro Junior as an attempt on Alfred E. Neuman like mascot

This book features various underground cartoonist (some famous and some not) having their take on Pro Junior

Very cool

Jay Lynch, Joe Pilati, Robert Crumb, S. Clay Wilson, Evert Geradts, Jay Kinney, Art Spiegelman, Justin Green, Jim Mitchell, Trina Robbins, Pete Poplaski, Peter Loft, Ned Sontag, Denis Kitchen, Dave Dozier, Wendel Pugh, Dave L. Herring, Bruce Walthers, Dale Kuipers, Skip Williamson, Joel Beck, Bill Griffith, Don Dohler, Peter Bramley

Published by Kitchen Sink 1971
